        (
            SELECT e.Id, e.Deceased, e.Gender
            FROM Entities AS e
            WHERE EXISTS (
                SELECT 1
                FROM Address AS a
                WHERE ((e.Id != NULL) && (e.Id == a.EntityId)) && a.Country IN (

                    FROM OPENJSON(@__countries_0) WITH (value nvarchar(max) '') AS c))

    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Address] AS [a0] ON [t].[Id] = [a0].[EntityId]
LEFT JOIN [Date] AS [d] ON [t].[Id] = [d].[EntityId]
LEFT JOIN [Name] AS [n] ON [t].[Id] = [n].[EntityId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [a0].[EntityId], [a0].[Id], [d].[EntityId], [d].[Id], [n].[EntityId]

        FROM [Name] AS [n]
        WHERE [e].[Id] = [n].[EntityId] AND COALESCE([n].[FirstName], N'') + N' ' + COALESCE([n].[MiddleName], N'') + N' ' + COALESCE([n].[Surname], N'') LIKE @__search_0_contains ESCAPE N'\') OR EXISTS (

            2 -> Dictionary<IProperty, int> { [Property: Address.EntityId (no field, string) Shadow Required PK FK AfterSave:Throw, 3], [Property: Address.Id (no field, int) Shadow Required PK AfterSave:Throw ValueGenerated.OnAdd, 4], [Property: Address.AddressLine (string), 5], [Property: Address.City (string), 6], [Property: Address.Country (string), 7] }
            3 -> 3
            4 -> 4
            5 -> Dictionary<IProperty, int> { [Property: Date.EntityId (no field, string) Shadow Required PK FK AfterSave:Throw, 8], [Property: Date.Id (no field, int) Shadow Required PK AfterSave:Throw ValueGenerated.OnAdd, 9], [Property: Date.DateType (string), 10], [Property: Date.Dates (DateTime?), 11] }
            6 -> 8

            8 -> Dictionary<IProperty, int> { [Property: Name.EntityId (no field, string) Shadow Required PK FK AfterSave:Throw, 12], [Property: Name.Id (no field, int) Shadow Required PK AfterSave:Throw ValueGenerated.OnAdd, 13], [Property: Name.FirstName (string), 14], [Property: Name.MiddleName (string), 15], [Property: Name.Surname (string), 16] }
            9 -> 12
            10 -> 13
        SELECT t.Id, t.Deceased, t.Gender, a.EntityId, a.Id, a.AddressLine, a.City, a.Country, d.EntityId, d.Id, d.DateType, d.Dates, n0.EntityId, n0.Id, n0.FirstName, n0.MiddleName, n0.Surname
        FROM 
        (
            SELECT e.Id, e.Deceased, e.Gender, (
                SELECT TOP(1) n.Surname
                FROM Name AS n
                WHERE (e.Id != NULL) && (e.Id == n.EntityId)) AS c
            FROM Entities AS e
            ORDER BY (
                SELECT TOP(1) n.Surname
                FROM Name AS n
                WHERE (e.Id != NULL) && (e.Id == n.EntityId)) DESC
            OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
        ) AS t
        LEFT JOIN Address AS a ON t.Id == a.EntityId
        LEFT JOIN Date AS d ON t.Id == d.EntityId
        LEFT JOIN Name AS n0 ON t.Id == n0.EntityId
        ORDER BY t.c DESC, t.Id ASC, a.EntityId ASC, a.Id ASC, d.EntityId ASC, d.Id ASC, n0.EntityId ASC),

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

        (
            SELECT e.Id, e.Deceased, e.Gender, (
                SELECT TOP(1) n.FirstName
                FROM Name AS n
                WHERE (e.Id != NULL) && (e.Id == n.EntityId)) AS c
            FROM Entities AS e

                SELECT TOP(1) n.FirstName
                FROM Name AS n

        LEFT JOIN Date AS d ON t.Id == d.EntityId
